# SmartQuizzer — Adaptive AI Quiz Generator

**FastAPI** backend + **Vite React** frontend + **Supabase** + **OpenAI GPT** + advanced ML pipeline.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Keys Required:**
> - **OpenAI API Key** (`sk-...`)
> - **Supabase Project URL** (`https://xxx.supabase.co`)
> - **Supabase Anon Key** (`eyJ...`)

> [!WARNING]
> **Frontend Hard Rules:**
> - ❌ **NO icon libraries** (no FontAwesome, Lucide, Heroicons, etc.) — use CSS shapes, Unicode characters, or hand-styled text labels only
> - ❌ **NO glow/neon effects** — no `box-shadow` glows, no neon outlines, no text-shadow glows
> - ❌ **NO blue/purple AI theme** — warm organic palette only
> - ✅ Animations via CSS `@keyframes` + `transition` only — subtle, physical (lift, slide, fade)
> - ✅ Both light mode (default) + dark mode with smooth toggle

---

## AI/ML/DL Features — Frontend + Backend Map

Each feature has **backend processing** AND **frontend visualization**:

| # | Feature | Backend (Python) | Frontend (React) |
|---|---------|-----------------|-------------------|
| 1 | **NLP Concept Extraction** | spaCy NER extracts entities/terms from content | Highlighted text display with extracted concepts as tags |
| 2 | **Smart Distractor Generation** | Sentence Transformers rank semantic similarity of wrong answers | Distractor quality score shown per MCQ option |
| 3 | **Text Complexity Scoring** | Flesch-Kincaid + vocabulary depth + sentence length → score | Animated complexity meter (CSS bar) on content upload |
| 4 | **BERTopic Topic Modeling** | Auto-cluster content into topic groups | Interactive topic chips that filter quiz generation |
| 5 | **Knowledge Graph** | NLP extracts concept→concept relationships as nodes/edges JSON | D3.js force-directed graph, draggable nodes, click to explore |
| 6 | **Performance Prediction** | Scikit-learn model: historical accuracy → predicted score per topic | Predicted accuracy bar per topic on dashboard |
| 7 | **Weak Area Detection** | Pattern analysis: error frequency × topic × difficulty | Weak-area cards with improvement suggestions |
| 8 | **Content Summarization** | GPT generates TL;DR + key takeaways | Summary card with expandable sections before quiz |
| 9 | **Topic Cluster Visualization** | t-SNE/UMAP on sentence embeddings → 2D coordinates | Plotly.js interactive scatter plot, hover for details |
| 10 | **Elo Rating System** | Chess-style rating update for users AND questions | Elo badge on profile + rating change animation on results |

