#### Core Files
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [main.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/main.py) | FastAPI app, CORS, router mounts |
| [config.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/config.py) | Env loading (OPENAI_API_KEY, SUPABASE_URL, etc.) |
| [database.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/database.py) | Supabase client init |
| [models.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/models.py) | Pydantic models for all entities |
| [schemas.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/schemas.py) | Request/response schemas |

#### Route Files
| Route | Endpoints |
|-------|-----------|
| [routes/auth.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/routes/auth.py) | register, login, get profile, update profile |
| [routes/content.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/routes/content.py) | upload (text/PDF), fetch URL, list, get, delete |
| [routes/quiz.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/routes/quiz.py) | generate quiz, list, get, submit answers, get results |
| [routes/analytics.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/routes/analytics.py) | performance data, topic stats, predictions, knowledge graph data |
| [routes/admin.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/routes/admin.py) | user list, platform analytics, question moderation, flagging |

#### AI/ML Service Files
| Service | What It Does |
|---------|-------------|
| [services/content_processor.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/services/content_processor.py) | PDF extraction, URL scraping, spaCy NER, text chunking, readability scoring |
| [services/question_generator.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/services/question_generator.py) | GPT question generation (4 types), Sentence Transformer distractor ranking |
| [services/adaptive_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/services/adaptive_engine.py) | Elo rating updates, difficulty matching, session adaptation |
| [services/ml_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/services/ml_engine.py) | BERTopic, performance prediction (sklearn), weak area detection, t-SNE, knowledge graph builder |
| [services/summarizer.py](file:///c:/Users/Radha%20Makwana/Desktop/Quiz_Generation/backend/services/summarizer.py) | GPT summarization, key takeaways, topic list |

