## Frontend — Vite React (`frontend/`)

#### Design System
**Light Mode** (default): cream bg `#FAF7F2`, terracotta primary `#C4654A`, forest green `#2D6A4F`, golden accent `#D4A054`
**Dark Mode**: navy charcoal `#1A1A2E`, warm salmon `#E07A5F`, sage green `#52B788`, soft gold `#F2CC8F`
**Fonts**: Inter (headings) + DM Sans (body)
**Icons**: CSS-only shapes (circles, arrows, checkmarks via `::before`/`::after` + `border` tricks), Unicode symbols, styled text labels

#### Animation Rules
- ✅ `translateY` lift on card hover (2-4px), `box-shadow` depth change (no glow)
- ✅ `opacity` + `translateY` for page/card entrances
- ✅ SVG `stroke-dasharray` for progress rings
- ✅ CSS `transform: scale()` for button press feedback
- ✅ `animation-delay` for staggered card loading
- ✅ Smooth `300ms` CSS variable transition for theme toggle
- ❌ No `text-shadow` glow, no neon `box-shadow`, no pulsing/glowing keyframes

#### Pages with AI/ML Features

| Page | AI/ML Frontend Features |
|------|------------------------|
| **Dashboard** | Elo badge, performance prediction bars, weak area cards, recommended topics |
| **Content Upload** | Complexity meter bar, auto-extracted concept tags, GPT summary preview |
| **Quiz Generator** | BERTopic topic chips for filtering, difficulty distribution preview |
| **Take Quiz** | Real-time Elo-based question selection, adaptive difficulty indicator |
| **Results** | Elo change display, topic breakdown chart (Recharts), weak area analysis, improvement suggestions |
| **Knowledge Explorer** | D3.js force graph (concepts), Plotly.js t-SNE scatter (topics) |
| **Analytics** | Performance prediction chart, difficulty progression timeline, response-time analysis |
| **Profile** | Elo history timeline, predicted accuracy per subject |

